Code Analyzers(integrating with py-charm)

Add this tools in "External Tools" settings in pycharm IDE settings

1) pylint

  parameters :   --reports=n --output-format=parseable $FilePath$
  working directory : $Projectpath$
  output filter : $FILE_PATH$\:$LINE$

2) pep8

  parameters : $FilePath$
  working directory : $FilePath$
  output filter : $FILE_PATH$\:$LINE$\:$COLUMN$\:.*

3) pyflakes

  parameters : $FilePath$
  working directory : $FilePath$
  output filter: $FILE_PATH$\:$LINE$
